The paper discusses the design of fuzzy inference systems using computational frameworks such as genetic-fuzzy systems, neuro-fuzzy systems, hierarchical fuzzy systems, evolving fuzzy systems, and multi-objective fuzzy systems. These frameworks are related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI), machine learning (cs.LG), neural networks (cs.NE), control systems (cs.SY), and fuzzy logic (cs.FL). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
